					<div class="csc-header csc-header-n1"><h4 class="csc-firstHeader"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">For which browsers are the pages optimized by  ?</font></font></h4></div><p><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">To visit our pages you will need one of the following browsers:
</font></font></p>
<p><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Mozilla Firefox - latest version </font></font><br><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Safari - latest version </font></font><br><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Google Chrome - latest version </font></font><br><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Opera - latest version </font></font><br><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Edge / IE - latest version
</font></font></p>
<p><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Javascript and cookies must be activated. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">In addition, we recommend installing the Flash plugin, which is already standard for the browsers mentioned. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Unfortunately, older browsers can not display our pages.</font></font></p>
<div class="csc-header csc-header-n1"><h4 class="csc-firstHeader"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Why do I need a Flash plugin on the   website?</font></font></h4></div><p><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">With the help of the Flash plugin, your browser is able to display Flash movies. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">As a rule, Flash is integrated into your browser. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Since we show flash movies on some pages, we recommend using such a plugin. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">However, you can also view our pages without Flash plugin if you want to do without the presentation of these films.</font></font></p>
<div class="csc-header csc-header-n1"><h4 class="csc-firstHeader"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Will my personal data be kept confidential?</font></font></h4></div><p><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">We place great value on the confidential treatment of your personal data. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">We naturally comply with the legal provisions on data protection. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">In addition, it is important to us that you always know what data we store and how we use it. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Your personal data will neither be sold to a third party or to third parties who are not part of the   Group.</font></font></p>
<div class="csc-header csc-header-n1"><h4 class="csc-firstHeader"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Is my data secure during data transfer?</font></font></h4></div><p><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">  places great emphasis on the security of the data transmission of sensitive customer information. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">The connection is private in the best sense, because its content is transmitted encrypted over the network using the certificate protocol SSL. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">This secure connection is received at the very moment when you enter the page to enter your personal data because https is losing performance significantly against http. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">The identity of the server (https) is fixed, which you can only see in the source text through data transmissions within a frame on many of our pages.</font></font></p>
				</div>
