				<h3 class="t3-js-accordeon-hd"><span><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">FAQs on the rental process</font></font></span></h3>
				<div class="t3-js-accordeon-content t3-accordeon-content" style="display: block;">
					<div class="csc-header csc-header-n1"><h4 class="csc-firstHeader"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">How can I find out about  's network?</font></font></h4></div><p><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Under the menu item "Stations", you will find every   station worldwide with details of the address and contact information, including opening times. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">The fastest way to get to your nearest   station is through our Stationsfinder. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">It offers you route planning and overview maps in one.</font></font></p>
<div class="csc-header csc-header-n1"><h4 class="csc-firstHeader"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">What does "Meet &amp; Greet" mean after the station name?</font></font></h4></div><p><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">This is not a physical rental station, but a meeting place where a   driver is waiting for you with your name plate and your   car. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">The advantage is obvious: you have no waiting times at the counter!</font></font></p>
<div class="csc-header csc-header-n1"><h4 class="csc-firstHeader"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">How do I reserve a   car?</font></font></h4></div><p><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Decide whether you can book your rental car online at </font></font><a href="http://www. .de/" target="_blank" class="external-link-new-window"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">www. .de</font></font></a><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"> , in one of Germany's 550   stations in person, by calling +49 (0) 180 6 66 66 66 (0.20 Euro / call from German landline, mobile phone rates max. 0.60 Euro / call) or book a travel agency.</font></font></p>
<div class="csc-header csc-header-n1"><h4 class="csc-firstHeader"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">What are the advantages of using the Internet?</font></font></h4></div><ul><li><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Real-time reservation, means for you the direct verification of your request for vehicle availability and immediate certification in the form of a reservation confirmation. </font></font></li><li><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Cheap internet rates, which are clearly under our offline conditions.</font></font></li><li><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Transparent pricing. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">We will show you at a glance your rental price including all applicable service packages.</font></font></li></ul>
<div class="csc-header csc-header-n1"><h4 class="csc-firstHeader"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Are the   Internettarife discountable?</font></font></h4></div><p><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Our Internettarife are already so cheaply calculated, that unfortunately we can not grant a discount. </font></font></p>
<div class="csc-header csc-header-n1"><h4 class="csc-firstHeader"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">How can I book the cheap weekend (Fri. 12 am - Mon. 9 am) and week tariffs (as of 5 days) from  ?</font></font></h4></div><p><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">After entering your reservation data, we automatically calculate the best online car rental price for you. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">This includes, of course, our favorable weekly and weekend packages.  </font></font></p>
<div class="csc-header csc-header-n1"><h4 class="csc-firstHeader"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">How can I keep up-to-date on   offers?</font></font></h4></div><p><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">A 14-day newsletter as well as the   news on this page always provide news and special offers for you. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">You will find the points under "News".  </font></font></p>
<div class="csc-header csc-header-n1"><h4 class="csc-firstHeader"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">How many hours in advance do I have to reserve my rental car on the Internet?</font></font></h4></div><p><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">A reservation is necessary about 2 hours before pick-up of the vehicle. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Please note the advance booking period of 24 hours for jeeps / convertibles. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Any other provisions will be communicated to you upon reservation of the rented vehicle.  </font></font></p>
<div class="csc-header csc-header-n1"><h4 class="csc-firstHeader"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Is it possible to cancel a reservation made?</font></font></h4></div><p><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Your reservation can be canceled at any time via the reservation number and the access code. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">The cancellation can be made under "Customer Center".  </font></font></p>
<div class="csc-header csc-header-n1"><h4 class="csc-firstHeader"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Can I rent a special vehicle model at  ?</font></font></h4></div><p><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">  offers the hire of groups, not of individual vehicles. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">A list of possible vehicle types for each rental country is given in the rental price calculation.
</font></font></p>
<p><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Alternative offers from  : </font></font><br><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">  luxury cars not only offers particularly high-quality vehicles for high demands. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">We offer you the special service, eg to procure exactly the vehicle model you have always dreamed of, would like to test it once or simply are used to driving. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Look for your car model and ask </font></font><a href="http://www. luxurycars.com/" target="_blank"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">us</font></font></a><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"> &nbsp;at </font><a href="http://www. luxurycars.com/" target="_blank"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">www. luxurycars.com</font></a><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"> or at our qualified   luxury cars team (+49 (0) 180 6677077 / 0.20 € per call from the German fixed network, mobile phone prices vary). </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">We will send you an offer immediately.&nbsp;</font></font></p>
