					<div class="csc-header csc-header-n1"><h4 class="csc-firstHeader"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Who is liable for breaches of the law during my rental?</font></font></h4></div><p><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">In accordance with the General Terms and Conditions (§I3), you are liable as a vehicle rental unrestricted for all costs and fees incurred in connection with traffic and administrative offenses. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">We provide the tenant data, as stated and accepted at the time of rental, to the requesting authority.  </font></font></p>
<div class="csc-header csc-header-n1"><h4 class="csc-firstHeader"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Does   calculate an expense hike for handling the penalty tickets?</font></font></h4></div><p><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">  calculates </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">an expense expense </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">according to the </font></font><a href="https://www. .de/informationen/agb/" class="internal-link"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">general</font></font></a><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"> terms and conditions </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">A copy of the authorities' request will be sent to you along with our letter.  </font></font></p>
<div class="csc-header csc-header-n1"><h4 class="csc-firstHeader"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Why is this fee charged?</font></font></h4></div><p><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">The calculated fee is an expense expense for the processing of a traffic offense. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">We usually receive very different letters from the authorities, which makes automation very limited. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">In the majority of cases, the data must be determined individually. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">The processing of the corresponding inquiries is associated with significant internal costs for  .
</font></font></p>
