<div class="csc-header csc-header-n1"><h4 class="csc-firstHeader"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Is the fine included in the expense allowance or do I have to pay extra? </font></font></h4></div><p><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Please pay the fine directly to the authority, if this has contacted you. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">There is no payment by  .  </font></font></p>
