</font></font></p>
<p><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"> The respective government requests are displayed for the tenancy agreements.  </font></font></p>
<div class="csc-header csc-header-n1"><h4 class="csc-firstHeader"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Can I circumvent the expense expense if I report the offense to you in advance?</font></font></h4></div><p><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">We would be happy to receive your information. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">However, this does not reduce the effort that we have to deal with processing the authorities. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">We apologize for any inconvenience.  </font></font></p>
<div class="csc-header csc-header-n1"><h4 class="csc-firstHeader"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">I received an invoice for an administrative offense. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">At the time I had already parked the car at the   branch.</font></font></h4></div><p><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">At most of our stores there is ample parking. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">If the vehicle has not been properly parked, this can result in a penalty. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">These are paid by   and are subsequently debited to the previous tenant plus the expense allowance.  </font></font></p>
<div class="csc-header csc-header-n1"><h4 class="csc-firstHeader"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">I did not cause the administrative offense, but only the rental car paid. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Do I still have to pay the penalty and expense expense?</font></font></h4></div><p><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Please inform the authority if the driver differs from the tenant's name. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">The expense allowance is automatically calculated by the renter of the vehicle and must be paid to  . </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">It is irrelevant who makes this referral. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">A separate letter to the actual cause is not sent.  </font></font></p>
